\operatorname{cov}(X,Y) = \mathbb{E}(XY) - (\mathbb{E}X)(\mathbb{E}Y) = \mathbb{E}(\mathbb{E}(XY \mid X)) - (\mathbb{E}X)(\mathbb{E}Y)
= \mathbb{E}(X\mathbb{E}(Y\mid X)) - (\mathbb{E}X)(\mathbb{E}Y)
= \mathbb{E}(X^2) - (\mathbb{E}X)(\mathbb{E}Y)
