\mathbb{E}(X)= \mathbb{E}(\mathbb{E}(X\mid Y)) = \mathbb{E}(Y)
\operatorname{cov}(X,Y) = \mathbb{E}(X^2) - (\mathbb{E}X)^2 = \operatorname{var}(X)
\operatorname{cov}(X,Y) = \operatorname{var}(Y)
